					<p>Yaroslav: Thanks for your comment! I've checked out redirecting a little bit, but right now it seems in php4 your only chance to check for it is to overwrite the AppController's redirect function to store the informaiton in the controller. php5 knows a function called headers_list which would do the trick, but there is no php4 version of it. I'll talk with the other devs and see if there is a way to make CakePHP a little bit more test friendly.</p>
<p>Support for asserting session data and cookies is planned as well.</p>
